_sText: This is a rock floating in the sky with a house built on it, some trees and other stuff. It contains mostly climbing spots but also some for barricading. Thanks to hipshot for the nice skybox texture! [Features:] - 64 spawn points - cubemaps - no falling damage (you get teleported back up) - climbing and barricading/camping spots - good framerate [Update History:] --- v2 (01.04.2010) --- v2 is still available for download here (for smaller servers). - Fixed invalid spawn points - Fixed falling damage bug (some players DID receive damage) - Added some more hiding spots - Improved design slightly in some places - Made one hiding spot easier accessible (the 3 small floating rocks) --- v3 (03.04.2010) --- - Enlarged the map - Connected various camping spots / made them easier accessible --- v4 (04.04.2010) --- - Made the tree easier accessible - Fixed a spot where you could get stuck - Players don't get stuck anymore when being teleported --- v5 (19.04.2010) --- - Added another barricading room inside the main rock - Made the camping spot inside the smaller rock easier accessible (there are more small crates instead of big ones now) - Some more minor changes [Known bug:] On a server where killed zombies respawn as humans the respawned humans get falling damage.. and thus die when they fall down. (Although I added an extra trigger in front of the teleports. There seems to be no solution for this problem) >> Click here to look for servers where this map is running! <<
